title: Gen. Jack Keane: Russia only Launching Token “Window-Dressing” Strikes in ISIS Areas – Video 10/4/15 | Tea Party
text:
(Before It's News)

Here is Gen. Jack Keane using a map of Syria to show what Russia and Vladimir Putin are up to in Syria. As the General shows, Russia has launched only a couple of “window-dressing” airstrikes in ISIS-controlled areas while concentrating their attacks on Free Syrian Army areas opposed to Syrian Dictator Assad.
Donald Trump said yesterday that Putin is “bombing the hell out of ISIS.” As Gen. Keane shows – NO he is NOT. Putin is only launching some token strikes in ISIS areas to give him cover for what he is really up to.
